current.name: First Aid Set In Pouch
current.metaTitle: Promotional First Aid Set In Pouch | National Pen IE
current.description: First Aid Sets are always an appreciated gift that could prove essential in unexpected situations. Show your customers and employees you care by adding these promotional first aid sets to your next campaign. This set includes a pouch with one front pocket, one black zipped main compartment and a belt loop on backside of pouch. It contains a triangle bandage, pbt bandage, alcohol pad, plasters, scissors, pin and tape.
